snippet.title: Assassin's Creed: Liberation HD Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Assassin's Creed: Liberation HD - preview interview with gameplay. Unless you're a PS Vita owner, chances are you missed last year's Assassin's Creed III: Liberation. But Liberation gets a second bite of the cherry next year with Assassin's Creed: Liberation HD, an updated, spruced-up version of the game with new missions. Watch on to find out all about Assassin's Creed: Liberation HD on Xbox 360 and why hero Aveline is the series' most exciting protagonist to date.
